{"tid":2175332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVBS民調：柯文哲聲望跌破32趴，為六都市長最低","createTime":"2020-08-26T11:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T18:55:34.000Z","uid":52658,"like":119,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9490d6ac19707c50d3ff0c3dabe9e93be34691","tid":2175332,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:52:18.000Z","msg":"蔡英文總統的聲望在兩年前九合一選後，下滑到15%的歷史低點，但之後逐漸回升，在總統大選前一個月回升至41%，勝選後一個月提升至五成以上（54%），3月25日達到六成，連任就職時至61%的近期高點，但本次調查再下滑近一成至52%，與選後一個月時五成多的 滿意度相當。顯示，近期防疫、振興經濟等政策爭議，可能有所影響。<br />\n<br />\n本次調查柯文哲聲望位居第十，由107年11月調查的61%，大幅下滑29個百分點，至 32%。交叉分析顯示，各年齡層對柯文哲的滿意度均呈現下滑，其中20-29歲及30-39歲下滑的幅度超過三成五，滿意度由八成左右分別降至47%及39%；40歲以上民眾不滿意柯文哲的比例達半數，60歲以上對柯文哲滿意度僅17%。<br />\n<br />\n前總統馬英九聲望30%，排名第11；國民黨主席江啟臣聲望為29%，排名居末<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tx07SqT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftx07SqT.png&h=4af8500b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nTvLD5W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnTvLD5W.png&h=1d674c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/HatePolitics/M.1598434453.A.439.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FHatePolitics%2FM.1598434453.A.439.html&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhath5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=906702f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/HatePolitics/M.1598434453.A.439.html</a>"},{"pid":"c91f138919de620e04fd80cfbd52b9139a87f2a1","tid":2175332,"uid":308486,"like":5,"dislike":21,"score":-16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:55:50.000Z","msg":"咁低居然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51120dd8cd7a65d10c949ec98d6700fc9de773bf","tid":2175332,"uid":52658,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"quote":{"pid":"c91f138919de620e04fd80cfbd52b9139a87f2a1","tid":2175332,"uid":308486,"like":5,"dislike":21,"score":-16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:55:50.000Z","msg":"咁低居然<img src=\"/assets/faces/no